Package: ffscrapr
Type: Package
Title: FFscrapR - R Client for Fantasy Football League APIs
Version: 0.0.4.9
Authors@R: person("Tan", "Ho", email = "tan@tanho.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package abstracts the code required to call various Fantasy Football APIs 
    (i.e. MFL, Sleeper, Fleaflicker, ESPN, Yahoo) and create methods that handle any authentication required, 
    form appropriate calls, and return tidy & predictable dataframes which can be easily connected to other sources.
